In summary, there's
three recommendations

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:18.079
we have for sign
in best practices.

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:21.754
First, adding an automatic
sign in upon game launch

00:04:21.754 --> 00:04:25.320
is our preferred method and one
that will provide the highest

00:04:25.320 --> 00:04:26.900
sign in rates.

00:04:26.900 --> 00:04:30.300
Second, add an automatic sign
in upon finishing the game

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:31.440
tutorial.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:33.970
This will immerse
users in the tutorial

00:04:33.970 --> 00:04:36.510
before asking them to login.

00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:39.390
Third, feature a sign
in button prominently

00:04:39.390 --> 00:04:41.500
upon launching
your game and avoid

00:04:41.500 --> 00:04:44.430
burying it behind menu screens.

